casebody.data:
Lamont Alexander WAGNER
v.
Anthony HATHAWAY, III. No. 526P04-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 23, 2007. Lamont A. Wagner, pro se. Joseph Ellis Herrin, Assistant Attorney General, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 9th day of August 2007 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Forsyth County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 23rd day of August 2007."
